1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 28=

3
00:00:50,660 --> 00:00:51,680
What are you trying to do?

4
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:54,420
Isn't the Commander
very important to you?

5
00:00:54,700 --> 00:00:57,100
He prepared all this for us himself.

6
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,380
Do you like it?

7
00:00:58,700 --> 00:00:59,820
He prepared this?

8
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,100
Where is he now?

9
00:01:08,540 --> 00:01:09,740
Does your husband

10
00:01:11,300 --> 00:01:12,820
know how beautiful you are?

11
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:16,380
What?

12
00:01:18,180 --> 00:01:19,500
Can't take it anymore?

13
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:22,340
Wasn't it you who said
that as long as I let him go,

14
00:01:23,780 --> 00:01:25,340
you'd do anything?

15
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:27,500
Then what exactly do you want?

16
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:30,220
Simple.

17
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:39,020
Show me

18
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:42,260
your most beautiful side

19
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:47,580
until I'm satisfied.

20
00:01:54,260 --> 00:01:55,380
There are people outside.

21
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:58,100
Doesn't that make it even more exciting?

22
00:01:59,980 --> 00:02:01,020
And one of those people

23
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:03,740
is your husband.

24
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:06,220
You don't mind him watching, do you?

25
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:10,059
I'm begging you,
please stop provoking him, alright?

26
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:10,819
Do you even realize

27
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:12,499
what kind of consequences
this will bring?

28
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:13,620
Consequences?

29
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:16,699
I rule Yancheng.

30
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,340
What consequences would I fear?

31
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:21,779
Zhuang Yunqiu, weren't you the one
who begged me to let him go?

32
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:22,819
Now I've granted your wish.

33
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:25,059
Isn't it perfect to let him stand
outside and guard the door for us?

34
00:02:25,060 --> 00:02:26,140
Make him speak!

35
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:29,539
Lu Shaoyuan!

36
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:30,700
Let her go!

37
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:32,180
She's my wife!

38
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:33,820
She can only belong to me!

39
00:02:34,180 --> 00:02:35,139
You can't touch her!

40
00:02:35,140 --> 00:02:36,740
Lu Shaoyuan, let go!

41
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:38,700
Lu Shaoyuan!

42
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:40,459
I'm begging you, Lu Shaoyuan.

43
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,379
Please...

44
00:02:41,380 --> 00:02:42,219
Stop provoking him,

45
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:42,699
alright?

46
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,780
Please.

47
00:02:45,820 --> 00:02:46,779
Miss Zhuang,

48
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:48,980
are you begging for your husband again?

49
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:50,500
Fine.

50
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:53,180
Zhuang Yunqiu, think about your child!

51
00:02:53,260 --> 00:02:54,900
Think about our child!

52
00:02:54,980 --> 00:02:56,980
Think about our child!

53
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,180
What?

54
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:02,940
Now you don't care
whether your husband lives or dies?

55
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,380
Isn't this enough already?

56
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:09,860
Not even close.

57
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:11,540
Zhuang Yunqiu,

58
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:13,780
I'm really curious.

59
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,219
During these six years,

60
00:03:15,220 --> 00:03:18,259
every time you shared his bed,

61
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:20,979
was there ever even a moment
when you thought of me?

62
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:23,580
Even for a moment?

63
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:25,620
Was there?

64
00:03:33,860 --> 00:03:35,540
Lu Shaoyuan, let her go!

65
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:37,579
Stay away from her!

66
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:38,700
Lu Shaoyuan!

67
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:48,300
That voice sounds wonderful.

68
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:50,540
Louder.

69
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:52,620
A little louder!

70
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,259
Lu Shaoyuan, what are you doing?

71
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:56,499
Let her go!

72
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:58,340
She's your sister in law!

73
00:04:03,420 --> 00:04:05,060
Sister in law?

74
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,379
Lu Shaoyuan!

75
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:09,980
Let go of your sister in law!

76
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:14,540
Get him out of here.

77
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:15,779
Lu Shaoyuan!

78
00:04:15,780 --> 00:04:17,380
Lu Shaoyuan!

79
00:04:21,860 --> 00:04:23,180
Let go!

80
00:04:30,980 --> 00:04:32,300
That's enough for today.

81
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,340
We'll continue tomorrow.

82
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:47,340
What should I do?

83
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:49,420
Xiaoxiao...

84
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:51,179
I'm so sorry.

85
00:04:51,180 --> 00:04:52,980
What am I supposed to do about Xiaoxiao?

86
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:08,739
Commander-in-Chief,

87
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:10,139
our wedding is coming up soon.

88
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:11,660
Why don't we go pick out
a wedding dress?

89
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,020
Alright.

90
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:14,340
We'll go after lunch.

91
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:19,260
Eat some food.

92
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:19,980
Mm.

93
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,739
Commander-in-Chief, Miss,

94
00:05:32,740 --> 00:05:33,660
please enjoy.

95
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:35,820
Who told you to make this?

96
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:42,379
I thought you liked it.

97
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:43,540
I don't.

98
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:47,860
Make it again.

99
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:50,819
Commander-in-Chief,

100
00:05:50,820 --> 00:05:52,299
I like fish.

101
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,900
Why don't we have fish instead?

102
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:55,820
Alright.

103
00:05:57,620 --> 00:05:58,380
Go make it.

104
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:04,420
Yes.

105
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,980
Commander-in-Chief, have some fruit.

106
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,220
Please enjoy.

107
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:40,980
Stop right there.

108
00:06:42,660 --> 00:06:44,660
Pick the bones out
of the fish for Miss Xue.

109
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,420
Commander-in-Chief,

110
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:50,540
how did you know I don't like
picking fish bones myself?

111
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:51,820
You're so good to me.

112
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:57,140
These past years,

113
00:06:57,420 --> 00:06:58,540
you've treated me even better.

114
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,140
I know.

115
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,980
What are you standing there for?

116
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:06,940
Pick the bones out.

117
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:12,500
Eat.

118
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,340
Done.

119
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:36,860
Did you even taste the fish

120
00:07:37,980 --> 00:07:39,020
before serving it?

121
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:41,580
What if it tastes bad?

122
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:48,260
Exactly.

123
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:49,900
What if you poisoned it?

124
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:53,100
Fine.

125
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:55,260
I'll eat it.

126
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:04,460
Why did you stop?

127
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,260
Isn't fish your favorite?

128
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:25,940
Keep eating.

129
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,619
You cooked it yourself,

130
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:48,420
yet even you look miserable eating it.

131
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:51,180
Now you've ruined everyone's appetite.

132
00:08:52,580 --> 00:08:53,580
Take it away.

133
00:08:58,980 --> 00:09:00,060
Commander-in-Chief,

134
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,020
come take a walk with me.

135
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:04,740
Alright.

136
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:06,900
We should go pick out
the wedding dress too.

137
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:21,299
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

138
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:22,100
Yunqiu...

139
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:23,180
Yunqiu!

140
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:24,500
Yunqiu...

141
00:09:25,060 --> 00:09:25,940
Yunqiu!

142
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:28,540
Yunqiu...

143
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,060
Yunqiu!

144
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:39,400
♪Past and future both fade away♪

145
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:45,920
♪Love is so strange,
the way it entangles me♪

146
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:51,800
♪I still haven't awakened,
though I know I shouldn't♪

147
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:56,379
♪Still gently holding onto the♪

148
00:09:56,380 --> 00:10:00,360
♪Happy game that began within a dream♪

149
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:02,900
♪Joy and pleasure♪

150
00:10:04,780 --> 00:10:09,470
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

151
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:16,100
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

152
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:20,180
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

153
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:23,530
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

154
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:28,820
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

155
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:35,130
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

156
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:41,790
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

157
00:10:42,330 --> 00:10:45,710
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

158
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:48,909
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

159
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:54,049
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

160
00:10:54,050 --> 00:10:58,369
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

161
00:10:58,370 --> 00:11:00,949
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

162
00:11:00,950 --> 00:11:03,229
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

163
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:06,779
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

164
00:11:06,780 --> 00:11:11,309
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

165
00:11:11,310 --> 00:11:13,840
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

166
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:15,929
♪Still I walk into♪

167
00:11:15,930 --> 00:11:19,529
♪The trap you set without regret♪

168
00:11:19,530 --> 00:11:23,579
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

169
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:26,159
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

170
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:28,319
♪A stand in can never cross♪

171
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:31,759
♪The shortest distance between us♪

172
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:36,730
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

173
00:11:36,890 --> 00:11:41,560
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

174
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:45,909
♪A substitute♪

175
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:50,910
♪Needs no reason♪

